## Product Endpoints

### 8) List Products / Get Product

#### Endpoint

/api/products/b{business_id}/

#### Method

GET

#### Auth

No (current code uses AllowAny)

#### Request Body

None

#### Query Parameters

| Param | Required | Notes                                              |
| ----- | -------- | -------------------------------------------------- |
| id    | No       | If provided, filters by product id within business |

#### Responses

| Status | Response                                |
| ------ | --------------------------------------- |
| 200    | Array of product objects                |
| 400    | {"message": "Business ID is required."} |
| 500    | {"error": "..."}                        |

### 9) Create Product

#### Endpoint

/api/products/b{business_id}/

#### Method

POST

#### Auth

No (current code uses AllowAny, but logic depends on request.user)

#### Request Body

| Field        | Type    | Required | Notes                                    |
| ------------ | ------- | -------- | ---------------------------------------- |
| product_name | string  | Yes      | Must be unique per user by current check |
| category     | integer | Yes      | Category id                              |
| unit_price   | number  | Yes      | Decimal value                            |
| quantity     | integer | Yes      | Stock quantity                           |
| user_id      | integer | Yes      | Required by service validation           |
| description  | string  | No       | Optional                                 |

#### Responses

| Status | Response                                                       |
| ------ | -------------------------------------------------------------- |
| 201    | {"message": "Product created successfully!", "product": {...}} |
| 400    | {"error": "Business ID is required"}                           |
| 400    | {"error": "You already have a product with this name."}        |
| 500    | {"error": "Error creating product: ..."}                       |

### 10) Update Product

#### Endpoint

/api/products/b{business_id}/

#### Method

PUT

#### Auth

No (current code uses AllowAny, but enforces product ownership by request.user)

#### Request Body

Partial product fields.

#### Query Parameters

| Param | Required | Notes      |
| ----- | -------- | ---------- |
| id    | Yes      | Product id |

#### Responses

| Status | Response                                                                 |
| ------ | ------------------------------------------------------------------------ |
| 200    | {"message": "Product updated successfully!", "product": {...}}           |
| 400    | {"error": "Business ID is required"}                                     |
| 400    | {"error": "Product ID is required"}                                      |
| 400    | {"error": "Invalid Product ID"}                                          |
| 404    | {"error": "Product not found or you do not have permission to edit it."} |

### 11) Delete Product

#### Endpoint

/api/products/b{business_id}/

#### Method

DELETE

#### Auth

No (current code uses AllowAny, but enforces product ownership by request.user)

#### Request Body

None

#### Query Parameters

| Param | Required | Notes      |
| ----- | -------- | ---------- |
| id    | Yes      | Product id |

#### Responses

| Status | Response                                                                   |
| ------ | -------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| 200    | {"message": "Product deleted successfully!"}                               |
| 400    | {"error": "Business ID is required"}                                       |
| 400    | {"error": "Product ID is required"}                                        |
| 404    | {"error": "Product not found or you do not have permission to delete it."} |

## Party Endpoints

### 12) List Parties / Get Party

#### Endpoint

/api/parties/b{business_id}/

#### Method

GET

#### Auth

Yes

#### Request Body

None

#### Query Parameters

| Param         | Required | Notes                                                        |
| ------------- | -------- | ------------------------------------------------------------ |
| id            | No       | Party id, returns single party with nested customer/supplier |
| category_type | No       | Customer or Supplier                                         |
| page          | No       | Paginated list page                                          |

#### Responses

| Status | Response                                    |
| ------ | ------------------------------------------- |
| 200    | Single party object or paginated party list |
| 404    | {"error": "Party not found"}                |

### 13) Create Party

#### Endpoint

/api/parties/b{business_id}/

#### Method

POST

#### Auth

Yes

#### Request Body

| Field          | Type    | Required | Notes                      |
| -------------- | ------- | -------- | -------------------------- |
| Category_type  | string  | Yes      | Customer or Supplier       |
| is_active      | boolean | No       | Default true               |
| name           | string  | Yes      | Required for practical use |
| email          | string  | No       | Customer duplicate check   |
| phone_no       | string  | No       | Customer duplicate check   |
| Customer_code  | string  | No       | Customer duplicate check   |
| code           | string  | No       | Supplier code              |
| address        | string  | No       | Customer only              |
| open_balance   | number  | No       | Customer only              |
| credit_limmit  | number  | No       | Customer only              |
| loyalty_points | integer | No       | Customer only              |
| referred_by    | string  | No       | Customer only              |
| notes          | string  | No       | Customer only              |

#### Responses

| Status | Response                                                           |
| ------ | ------------------------------------------------------------------ |
| 201    | Customer or supplier created response with party and nested object |
| 400    | {"error": "Invalid Category. Must be 'Customer' or 'Supplier'"}    |
| 400    | Duplicate customer/supplier error with existing object             |

### 14) Update Party

#### Endpoint

/api/parties/b{business_id}/

#### Method

PUT

#### Auth

Yes

#### Request Body

Partial customer or supplier fields.

#### Query Parameters

| Param | Required | Notes    |
| ----- | -------- | -------- |
| id    | Yes      | Party id |

#### Responses

| Status | Response                                                                                                 |
| ------ | -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| 200    | {"message": "Customer updated successfully!", ...} or {"message": "Supplier updated successfully!", ...} |
| 400    | {"error": "Party ID is required"}                                                                        |
| 400    | {"error": "No related customer or supplier found"}                                                       |
| 404    | {"error": "Party not found"}                                                                             |

