| Param | Required | Notes               |
| ----- | -------- | ------------------- |
| page  | No       | Paginated list page |

#### Responses

| Status | Response                             |
| ------ | ------------------------------------ |
| 200    | Paginated list of billing objects    |
| 400    | {"error": "Business ID is required"} |

### 21) Create Billing

#### Endpoint

/api/billing/b{business_id}/

#### Method

POST

#### Auth

Yes

#### Request Body

| Field          | Type    | Required | Notes                          |
| -------------- | ------- | -------- | ------------------------------ |
| business_id    | integer | Yes      | Must match URL business        |
| invoice_number | string  | Yes      | Unique                         |
| payment_method | integer | Yes      | Payment method id              |
| invoice_status | string  | No       | Paid, Unpaid, Pending, Draft   |
| party          | integer | No       | Party id                       |
| invoice_date   | string  | No       | YYYY-MM-DD                     |
| due_date       | string  | No       | YYYY-MM-DD                     |
| total_amount   | number  | No       | Decimal                        |
| paid_amount    | number  | No       | Decimal                        |
| due_amount     | number  | No       | Decimal                        |
| discount       | number  | No       | Decimal                        |
| tax            | number  | No       | Decimal                        |
| sub_total      | number  | No       | Decimal                        |
| notes          | string  | No       | Optional                       |
| items          | array   | Yes      | Must include at least one item |

Billing item object fields:

| Field               | Type    | Required | Notes                 |
| ------------------- | ------- | -------- | --------------------- |
| item                | integer | Yes      | Product id            |
| quantity            | integer | Yes      | Item quantity         |
| rate                | number  | Yes      | Unit rate             |
| discount_percentage | number  | No       | Default 0             |
| tax_percentage      | number  | No       | Default 13            |
| total_price         | number  | Yes      | Persisted as provided |

#### Responses

| Status | Response                                                       |
| ------ | -------------------------------------------------------------- |
| 201    | {"message": "Billing created successfully!", "billing": {...}} |
| 400    | {"error": "Business ID is required"}                           |
| 400    | {"error": "At least one billing item is required."}            |
| 400    | Serializer validation errors                                   |

### 22) Update Billing

